"The world "out there" won't change until the world "in here" does." ~ Deepak Chopra
"The three things you can offer your children to change them: attention, appreciation and affection." ~ Deepak Chopra
"To define yourself is to limit yourself. Without labels you remain the infinite being." ~ Deepak Chopra
